{"tid":1538154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚嘢撤回呀 冇撚嘢呀?","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:27.000Z","uid":90010,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28af41eddb72ea172181a11ecf88242786b237ec","tid":1538154,"uid":90010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「五大訴求，缺一不可！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>少一個都唔得，唔係齋䁯！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「驅逐共黨，捍衛我城！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>提大家要企硬，同一理念嚟！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「光復香港，時代革命！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係夢，係行動！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">辛辛苦苦，搏晒老命打咗3個月，<br />\n<br />\n我都知大家好攰，對前路好迷茫，<br />\n<br />\n頂住呀，唔可以放棄，我哋冇時間再抖。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WE&rsquo;RE AT A POINT OF NO RETURN<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得呀？！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家對家求其䁯句撤回就讓步，<br />\n<br />\n對唔對得住咁多位義士、被捕手足、傷者！？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ed8794fe3fae1949444df9a802c54df6f4ecd1c0","tid":1538154,"uid":121869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁凌杰先生 (35歲) - 15/6/2019<br />\n<br />\n盧曉欣小姐 (21歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\n<br />\nZhita Wu (29歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\n<br />\n麥小姐 (28歲) - 3/7/2019<br />\n<br />\n梅先生 (32歲) - 5/7/2019<br />\n<br />\n范先生 (26歲) - 22/7/2019<br />\n<br />\nCalvin 郭先生 (25歲) - 27/8/2019<br />\